* &quot;Hymenophyllaceae&quot;, 1845 – Monograph on Hymenophyllaceae.
* &quot;Supplementum Tentaminis Pteridographiae&quot;, 1847.
* &quot;Die Gefässbündel im Stipes der Farrn&quot;, 1848 – The vascular bundles in the stipes of ferns.

