<doc id="1010692" wikidata="Q1311171" url="?curid=1010692" title="Football 7-a-side at the 2004 Summer Paralympics">
<text>[[CP football|7-a-side Football]] at the [[2004 Summer Paralympics]] took place at the Olympic Hockey Centre in Athens. The sport was open to contestants with cerebral palsy. Matches were 30 minutes each way.

The tournament was won by the team representing .

